Package: secureeval
Title: Evaluation and Benchmarking Framework for R LLM Agents
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ian", "Flores Siaca", , "iflores.siaca@hey.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Evaluation and benchmarking framework for R LLM agents. Test
    agents against known scenarios, score guardrail accuracy with
    precision, recall, and F1 metrics, run regression tests, and compare
    runs across iterations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ian-flores/secureeval
